ic\">Ser├ís redirigido para confirmar tu pedido.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</aside>\n</div>\n</main>\n<!-- Footer -->\n<footer class=\"w-full py-xl px-lg grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto border-t border-outline-variant/20 bg-surface-container-lowest mt-xl\">\n<div class=\"md:col-span-1 space-y-md\">\n<h2 class=\"font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary\">Ranch VCP</h2>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">┬® 2024 Ranch VCP. Comida fuerte para noches con hambre.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-sm\">\n<p class=\"font-label-md text-label-md uppercase text-gold\">Explorar</p>\n<a class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#\">Inicio</a>\n<a class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#\">Men├║</a>\n<a class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#\">Reservas</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-sm\">\n<p class=\"font-label-md text-label-md uppercase text-gold\">Sucursales</p>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">Uruguay - Av. Principal 123</p>\n<p class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">Libertad - Esquina Calma 456</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-sm\">\n<p class=\"font-label-md text-label-md uppercase text-gold\">Legal</p>\n<a class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#\">T├®rminos y Condiciones</a>\n<a class=\"font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"#\">Pol├¡tica de Privacidad</a>\n</div>\n</footer>\n<script>\n        // Smooth transition for category links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                const targetId = this.getAttribute('href');\n                const targetElement = document.querySelector(targetId);\n                const headerOffset = 180;\n                const elementPosition = targetElement.getBoundingClientRect().top;\n                const offsetPosition = elementPosition + window.pageYOffset - headerOffset;\n\n                window.scrollTo({\n                    top: offsetPosition,\n                    behavior: \"smooth\"\n                });\n\n                // Update active state in category bar\n                document.querySelectorAll('.sticky.top-\\\\[88px\\\\] a').forEach(link => {\n                    link.classList.remove('text-gold', 'border-b-2', 'border-gold');\n                    link.classList.add('text-on-surface-variant');\n                });\n                this.classList.add('text-gold', 'border-b-2', 'border-gold');\n                this.classList.remove('text-on-surface-variant');\n            });\n        });\n\n        // Simple scroll spy for category highligthing (conceptual)\n        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {\n            const sections = ['burgers', 'pizzas', 'lomos'];\n            let current = \"\";\n            \n            sections.forEach(section => {\n                const element = document.getElementById(section);\n                if(element) {\n                    const sectionTop = element.offsetTop - 200;\n                    if(pageYOffset >= sectionTop) {\n                        current = section;\n                    }\n                }\n            });\n\n            if(current) {\n                document.querySelectorAll('.sticky.top-\\\\[88px\\\\] a').forEach(link => {\n                    link.classList.remove('text-gold', 'border-b-2', 'border-gold');\n                    link.classList.add('text-on-surface-variant');\n                    if(link.getAttribute('href') === `#${current}`) {\n                        link.classList.add('text-gold', 'border-b-2', 'border-gold');\n                        link.classList.remove('text-on-surface-variant');\n                    }\n                });\n            }\n        });\n    </script>\n</body></html>"}